high_descs: Go to the sink on the other side of the room.
Pick up the apple from the sink.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave and then take it out.
Turn right to face the toaster.
Put the apple on the counter next to the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the counter.

high_descs: Go left to stand in front of the sink.
Pick the apple up out of the sink.
Go left and face the counter with the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, shut the door, open the door and take the apple out and shut the door.
Turn to the right to face the counter near the toaster.
Put the apple on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go into the kitchen to the right, then face the sink on the left.
Pick up the apple in the sink.
Go to the microwave on the left.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it, then remove the apple and close the microwave.
Turn to the right toward the toaster.
Place the apple on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Cook an apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to the sink.
Get the apple in the sink.
Turn left and head to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, turn it on, then get the apple in the microwave.
Turn right to face the toaster.
Put the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot apple on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the sink.
Pick up the apple.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Heat the apple.
Turn to the right.
Put the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the counter.
